svs 21.04.2011 20:50:39 +0300 - build 1983

1. Mantis#0001751: Menu creation in macro
   A macrofunction is added, Menu.Show()
     S=Menu.Show(Items[,Title[,Flags[,FindOrFilter[,X[,Y]]]]])
   see the Encyclopedia for the description.

